reports.title: Response (fed_request_city_org_patient-1)
reports.query:
MATCH (n:CityOrgPatient)
  WHERE n.request_id = "fed_request_city_org_patient-1"
RETURN [n.pt, n.organization_city, n.organization_name] AS name, n.patient_count AS count

reports.title: Request
reports.query:
CREATE (record:FR_CityOrgPatient) 
    SET
        record.request_id = "fed_request_city_org_patient-1",
        record.city = "Toronto",
        record.timestamp = apoc.date.currentTimestamp()
RETURN 
  record.request_id AS request_id,
  record.city AS city

reports.title: Request
reports.query:
CREATE (record:FR_CityOrgPatientVisit) 
    SET
        record.request_id = "fed_request_city_org_patient_visit-1",
        record.city = "Toronto",
        record.timestamp = apoc.date.currentTimestamp()
RETURN 
  record.request_id AS request_id,
  record.city AS city

reports.title: Response (fed_request_city_org_patient_visit-1)
reports.query:
MATCH (n:CityOrgPatientVisit)
  WHERE n.request_id = 'fed_request_city_org_patient_visit-1'
RETURN n.patient_id AS patient_id, n.encounter_count AS visits, n.organization_name AS organization, n.organization_city AS city
ORDER BY patient_id, city, organization

reports.title: Request
reports.query:
CREATE (record:FR_CityYearTopProc) 
    SET
        record.request_id = "fed_request_city_year_top_proc-1",
        record.city = "Mississauga",
        record.procedure_1 = "171207006", 
        record.procedure_2 = "430193006", 
        record.procedure_3 = "710841007", 
        record.timestamp = apoc.date.currentTimestamp()
RETURN record.city AS city, [record.procedure_1, record.procedure_2, record.procedure_3] AS procedures

reports.title: Response
reports.query:
MATCH (n:CityYearTopProc)
RETURN n.year AS year, n.procedure_1 AS procedure_1, n.procedure_2 AS procedure_2, n.procedure_3 AS procedure_3 ORDER BY year
